# Service configs that may contain production secrets
**/conf/server.yaml
**/conf/server.build.yaml
**/config/server.yaml
**/config/server.local.yaml
**/config/server.prod.yaml
**/config/*.local.yaml
**/config/*.prod.yaml
**/config/*.secret.yaml
gofurry-rag/config/server.yaml

